---
title: Sautéed Shrimp and Collard Greens over Cheddar Grits
description: Shrimp and grits is one of the most iconic Southern dishes. There are countless variations, but ours incorporates another Southern staple: collard greens! This unique veggie is ofen given a bad rep when prepared incorrectly – but a quick sauté over high heat is all it needs to truly shine!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sauteed-shrimp-5857d50b.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sauteed-shrimp-158dd00d.pdf
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
course: main course
cuisine: North America
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  calories: 458 kcal
  fat: 19 g
  saturated fat: 7 g
  carbohydrates: 44 g
  sugar: 5 g
